text: Roderbach or Röderbach may refer to: *Roderbach (Kyll), a river of North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany, downstream called Langbach, a tributary of the Kyll *Röderbach (Aschaff), a river of Bavaria, Germany, tributary of the Aschaff *Röderbach (Hasel), a river of Hesse, Germany, tributary of the Hasel
title: Roderbach
